prerequisites.environment_setup:
Node.js 22 (`engines.node: ">=22.0.0"`, Dockerfile `FROM node:22-bookworm-slim`). pnpm 9.15.0 enforced via `packageManager: pnpm@9.15.0` and corepack in the Dockerfile. Docker + Docker Compose for the local stack: `docker-compose up -d` brings up:
- DynamoDB Local / ministack (LocalStack) on :4566 — note: the actual image is `nahuelnucera/ministack`, not vanilla `localstack`; it bundles DynamoDB Local + SQS + STS + KMS + CloudWatch + ECR. The init script `infra/localstack/init/01-create-resources.sh` creates the SQS / STS / KMS / CloudWatch artefacts (causeflow DynamoDB table with PITR + 3 GSIs, 4 SQS queues + 4 DLQs, KMS alias `alias/causeflow-token-encryption`);
- Redis 7 Alpine on :6379;
- Langfuse (local) on :3001 — `langfuse/langfuse:2` + `langfuse-worker` with postgres:16-alpine on :5432;
- ghcr.io/vectorize-io/hindsight:latest on :8888/:9999;
- plus a set of customer sample services (order, payment, billing, notification, marketplace catalog/order/fulfillment) used for end-to-end investigation scenarios;
- and a `causeflow-relay` container that builds `core/relay` and connects back to the control plane over WSS.
Local env files: `.env.example` (documentation, pinned older defaults), `.env.localstack` (overrides for ministack), `.env.e2e` (E2E), `.env.smoke` (smoke), `.envrc` (per-developer shell — us-east-2). Env files: .env.example, .env.localstack, .env.e2e, .env.smoke, .envrc are the canonical local config bundle. Dev entrypoint: `pnpm dev` runs `tsx watch --env-file=.env.dev src/main.ts`. Lint, typecheck, unit tests, integration tests, and invariant check are all first-class scripts: `pnpm lint`, `pnpm typecheck`, `pnpm test:run`, `pnpm test:integration`, `pnpm test:e2e`, `pnpm test:smoke`, `pnpm test:eval`, `pnpm lint-invariants`. Deploy uses AWS CDK (`infra/cdk/package.json`, stacks at `infra/cdk/lib/bootstrap-stack.ts` and `infra/cdk/lib/causeflow-stack.ts`). CI is GitHub Actions (`.github/workflows/ci.yml`, `deploy.yml`, `eval.yml`). The `relay/` subdirectory is a separate git submodule registered in `.harness/projects.json` and is not part of `core`'s Work Items.
